{"tid":234020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聚陰氣]西九龍中心女子攀欄跳樓　撞穿安全網傷重亡","createTime":"2017-05-08T03:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T06:46:15.000Z","uid":29609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad387a878a43923657c5c53d3238a0b7a4272f14","tid":234020,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:06:16.000Z","msg":"西九龍中心有女子墮樓！早上8時許，一名50餘歲女子突從深水埗欽州街西九龍中心商場6樓高處墮下，撞穿安全網，直墮地面重傷淌血，陷入昏迷，一隻波鞋飛脫。救護員接報到場，為事主搶救，惜終告不治。商場職員在場撐起帳棚。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員在現場檢獲遺書及一張膠櫈，相信她於6樓踩櫈攀過欄河跳下，經初步調查後，得悉事主患病，不排她他因病厭世，事件無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/mobile/bkn-20170508084251674-0508_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170508%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170508084251674-0508_00822_001.html&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0bff7ad2\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/mobile/bkn-20170508084251674-0508_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"59d826c29cb2851bebfd0f9ecc2c8fbd28d8bc69","tid":234020,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4704e5272745fb00686d7a61daf4d0da5acf3328","tid":234020,"uid":266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:17:04.000Z","msg":"以為old news<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c3ae04a03277b382d3e1bd907268a186c6e88d","tid":234020,"uid":34140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:38:16.000Z","msg":"其實個安全網會穿咁仲有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aba31bca32dbf8afa5753b976d5768a6affee81","tid":234020,"uid":78574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T03:39:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實個安全網會穿咁仲有咩用<img src=\